      "content": "i just dont see the point anymore. everything i do just makes things worse for my wife and the kids. i look at the bills and i just feel like a parasite. if i wasn't here, they wouldn't have to worry about my mistakes or how much i cost them every month. it feels like the only way to actually help them is to just... not be a problem anymore.",
